androidx.test.orchestrator.listeners

Class TextListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.test.orchestrator.listeners.OrchestrationRunListener
      • androidx.test.orchestrator.listeners.TextListener

  • public class TextListener
extends OrchestrationRunListener
    Reimplementation of org.junit.TextListener that accepts AndroidTestOrchestrator compatible objects.

    OrchestrationResultPrinter is a near line by line copy of InstrumentationResultPrinter, and since InstrumentationResultPrinter relies on org.junit.internal.TextListener, this class exists for the OrchestrationResultPrinter to rely on, until such time as we can resolve b/35394729 and unify their expertise.

Generated javadoc for the new package structure to make it clearer which packages are bundled with the Android operating system, and which are packaged with your app's APK. Going forward, the android.* package hierarchy will be reserved for Android packages that ship with the operating system; other packages will be issued in the new androidx.* package hiearchy.
